<subSubSection pageId="24" pageNumber="25" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="24.[151,1436,898,1084]" pageId="24" pageNumber="25">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,326,1018,1044]" pageId="24" pageNumber="25">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Species with peculiar dorsal parttern consisting of four large orange maculae on elytra. Prehensor very long and thin.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
